001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonCreator;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
005import org.bitcoinj.base.Coin;
006
007import java.math.BigDecimal;
008
009/**
010 * POJO for `getinfo` RPC response.
011 */
012public class ServerInfo {
013    private final int version;
014    private final int protocolversion;
015    private final int walletversion;
016    private final Coin balance;
017    private final int blocks;
018    private final int timeoffset;
019    private final int connections;
020    private final String proxy;
021    private final BigDecimal difficulty;
022    private final Boolean testnet;
023    private final int keypoololdest;
024    private final int keypoolsize;
025    private final Coin paytxfee;
026    private final Coin relayfee;
027    private final String errors;
028
029    @JsonCreator
030    public ServerInfo(@JsonProperty("version")          int version,
031                      @JsonProperty("protocolversion")  int protocolversion,
032                      @JsonProperty("walletversion")    int walletversion,
033                      @JsonProperty("balance")          Coin balance,
034                      @JsonProperty("blocks")           int blocks,
035                      @JsonProperty("timeoffset")       int timeoffset,
036                      @JsonProperty("connections")      int connections,
037                      @JsonProperty("proxy")            String proxy,
038                      @JsonProperty("difficulty")       BigDecimal difficulty,
039                      @JsonProperty("testnet")          Boolean testnet,
040                      @JsonProperty("keypoololdest")    int keypoololdest,
041                      @JsonProperty("keypoolsize")      int keypoolsize,
042                      @JsonProperty("paytxfee")         Coin paytxfee,
043                      @JsonProperty("relayfee")         Coin relayfee,
044                      @JsonProperty("errors")           String errors) {
045        this.version = version;
046        this.protocolversion = protocolversion;
047        this.walletversion = walletversion;
048        this.balance = balance;
049        this.blocks = blocks;
050        this.timeoffset = timeoffset;
051        this.connections = connections;
052        this.proxy = proxy;
053        this.difficulty = difficulty;
054        this.testnet = testnet;
055        this.keypoololdest = keypoololdest;
056        this.keypoolsize = keypoolsize;
057        this.paytxfee = paytxfee;
058        this.relayfee = relayfee;
059        this.errors = errors;
060    }
061
062    public int getVersion() {
063        return version;
064    }
065
066    public int getProtocolversion() {
067        return protocolversion;
068    }
069
070    public int getWalletversion() {
071        return walletversion;
072    }
073
074    public Coin getBalance() {
075        return balance;
076    }
077
078    public int getBlocks() {
079        return blocks;
080    }
081
082    public int getTimeoffset() {
083        return timeoffset;
084    }
085
086    public int getConnections() {
087        return connections;
088    }
089
090    public String getProxy() {
091        return proxy;
092    }
093
094    public BigDecimal getDifficulty() {
095        return difficulty;
096    }
097
098    public Boolean getTestnet() {
099        return testnet;
100    }
101
102    public int getKeypoololdest() {
103        return keypoololdest;
104    }
105
106    public int getKeypoolsize() {
107        return keypoolsize;
108    }
109
110    public Coin getPaytxfee() {
111        return paytxfee;
112    }
113
114    public Coin getRelayfee() {
115        return relayfee;
116    }
117
118    public String getErrors() {
119        return errors;
120    }
121}
